🌟Thrilled to announce that I have embarked on a new journey ! 🌟

I've just started my final year internship at KPMG - Tech Solutions  as a Consultant Intern in the IT Advisory department! 🚀
Grateful for this opportunity and excited for the experiences and growth that lie ahead!💼 💡  

#KPMG #ITAdvisory #InternshipJourney #consulting

Dear Network,

I am thrilled to announce that I have recently joined Sofrecom Tunisie as a QA Automation Engineer! 
I want to extend my sincere gratitude to the entire team for their trust and support.

Here's to the beginning of a new adventure! 🚀 
#NewBeginnings #CareerJourney

🎓 100 pages, 6 months of research and 196 coffees later, I successfully graduated with a master's degree in "Marketing Intelligence and Strategic Watch" ✨.

Working on 'Elaborating a Marketing Strategy' for a product leveraging AI and Computer Vision was an exciting journey and an in-depth exploration. 
This all began during my internship at InstaDeep, a place I now proudly call my second home. 

A heartfelt thank you to my professional supervisor Sabrine Ben ali and my academic supervisor Mohja Kammoun whom their  mentorship and invaluable insights were instrumental in making this happen.
I am profoundly grateful for their faith in me and for their continuous support 🙏❤️.

Big thanks to everyone who made this journey happen. Your support meant the world to me. 
Now, with  this milestone done, I'm all set for new adventures and lots more learning ahead 🙌.

Nov. 05, 2023, officially GRADUATED!
I want to dedicate this achievement to all of you: To all those who have inspired me, to all those who trusted me, supported me, and believed in me, thank you...
To my managers: Dr. Ainhoa Llorente, mentors: Marwen Khazri, Meher Bnouni, Ahmed Cheikh Rouhou, and work colleagues with whom I worked, learned from, and grew with, forever grateful for all that I have learned from you.
To all my professors who were instrumental in my learning journey at Esprit School of Business, IHEC Carthage I have attended.
Today, I am thrilled to share that I have finally and officially graduated with high honors as a Business Analyst from the Esprit School of Business.
Reflecting on the past seven years of university, from having to obtain a master's degree in Supply Chain Management from IHEC Carthage to obtaining a master's degree in business Analysis. I have had the opportunity to volunteer, and be a part of various student clubs and organizations, wear many hats, and dabble in different fields ranging from a supply manager to a business analyst...
In addition to my academic pursuits, I have been fortunate to embark on internships with different companies and organizations InstaDeep, KPMG, TheSparksFoundation, Brandee...
Each experience has been a unique building block in shaping who I am today, personally and professionally. I am deeply grateful for the knowledge,
skills, and countless opportunities these organizations provided me during my student journey.
I am hopeful and excited about the future, and I can't wait to continue to learn and give back.

Reflecting on the end of an incredible journey! 🎓 My graduation internship at InstaDeep has been a rewarding blend of challenges and achievements, shaping a solid foundation for my career. 🚀

I'm deeply appreciative of Instadeep for granting me this invaluable opportunity, and I extend my heartfelt thanks to my esteemed mentors, Seif Dassi and Anwer Ammar , for their unwavering guidance during this enriching 6-month experience. 🙏

[#Stages]👉Inetum recrute des stagiaires d'été!
✅Cet été, rejoignez #Inetum pour enrichir votre formation par une expérience dans une multinationale !
📣Nous serons ravis de vous accueillir.
👉Nous recherchons des stagiaires pour :
☑️Travailler sur des projets internes en Transformation Digitale.
☑️Participer à l'élaboration d'environnement interne AGIRH.
☑️Aider à la planification, la synchronisation des étapes d’un projet et l’ensemble des tâches de PMO.
☑️Participer activement à la gestion de l'évènementiel et contribuer à des projets de communication Internes et externes.
☑️Contribuer au classement, à la saisie comptable ainsi qu’à la facturation.
🔔Postulez📧stages@inetum.tn en indiquant le thème qui vous intéresse.
📢Rejoignez-nous!
